*Duboko* se zavukla u toplu posteljinu. (She burrowed deep into the warm bedding.)

Njena misao je bila *duboka*. (Her thought was deep.)

*Duboko* sam udahnula i zatvorila oči. (I took a deep breath and closed my eyes.)

*Duboko* je zakopano u zemlju. (It is buried deep in the ground.)

*Duboko* u srcu osećam da će sve biti u redu. (Deep down in my heart, I feel that everything will be alright.)